messages.message:
*4/21-4/24 Recruiting Update*

• 39% pass-through rate on technical phone screens (R1's), so our upper funnel adjustments have put us back closer to the industry average :yayfox: 
• 7 virtual onsites (R2's) upcoming
• 1 offer for FE in the approval process :woohoo: 
• 1000 resumes still in the pipeline that need to be processed
• outbound sourcing underway with about 10% response rate so far
lastly, appreciate everyone for going above and beyond with interview workload this week and in the coming weeks. special shoutout to @danny.lan for taking on 4 interviews during this 4-day week :sparkles:
